name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Warren ARSAD, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of September, 2008, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus is DENIED. The Application for Leave to Amend Writ of Habeas Corpus is DISMISSED AS MOOT.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
